    "Other Infrastructural ImprovementsThe original VerilogEval benchmark contained all problems in a monolithic JSONL format.",
    "This is efficient to run, but inefficient to inspect manually using a text editor.",
    "In the improved benchmark, each problem was split into a set of files, including problem prompts, module interfaces, and test benches.",
